code: @Deployment public static Archive<?> createSpringBootPackage() throws Exception {     return ArquillianPackager.springBootPackage(createTestConfig()). }
public static ITestConfig createTestConfig() {     return new ITestConfigBuilder().module(inferModuleName(CamelTwitterTest.class)).unitTestInclusionPattern(".*UriConfigurationTest$").build(). }
